{"id":"fish-hooks","term":"Fish-hooks","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Were used for catching fish (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Amos 4:2\">Amos 4:2</a>; comp. <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Isaiah 37:29\">Isa. 37:29</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Jeremiah 16:16\">Jer. 16:16</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezekiel 29:4\">Ezek. 29:4</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Job 41:1\">Job. 41:1</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Job 41:2\">2</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Matthew 17:27\">Matt. 17:27</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Amos 4:2","Isaiah 37:29","Jeremiah 16:16","Ezekiel 29:4","Job 41:1","Job 41:2","Matthew 17:27"]}